query:
SELECT 
  bd.*,
  e.name as employee_name,
  e.code as employee_code,
  b.name as branch_name
FROM bonusDetails bd
JOIN employees e ON bd.employeeId = e.id
JOIN branches b ON bd.branchId = b.id
WHERE b.name LIKE '%طويق%'
AND bd.weekNumber = 3
AND bd.year = 2026
AND bd.month = 1;
